# tar@6.2.1 is a transitive dependency of @expo/cli (Expo SDK 52 dev tooling).
# It never ships in the app binary or runs on the backend — it's only used on
# developer machines/CI to extract prebuild templates. tar@7 fixes these CVEs
# but breaks @expo/cli ("tar.extract is undefined"), so it stays pinned at
# 6.2.1 (see mobile/package.json overrides) until the Expo SDK upgrade.
